"{\"uid\": \"thepinknews.com-2024-07-29-tom-daley-wins-silver-paris-2024-olympics-loses-gold-diving\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Tom Daley, who is gay, and his diving partner Noah Williams won silver at the Paris 2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 98, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 9, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.462084947852723e-48, \"text\": \"Tom Daley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\"}, {\"begin\": 46, \"end\": 59, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\", \"score\": 0.999998273608197, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Williams\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Getty)  Tom Daley and his diving partner Noah Williams have won a silver medal in the men's 10m synchronised platform diving final at the Paris 2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 99, \"to\": 258, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 108, \"end\": 117, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.462084947852723e-48, \"text\": \"Tom Daley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\"}, {\"begin\": 141, \"end\": 154, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\", \"score\": 0.999998273608197, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Williams\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 30-year-old queer athlete,Team GB flag-bearerand prolific knitter made his return to the Olympics for the fifth time today (29 July), as he attempted to defend his title in the event.\", \"from\": 260, \"to\": 447, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 290, \"end\": 297, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.6095890530024578, \"rank\": 0.6404481363281779, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_2012_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Daley won the gold alongside his then partner Matty Lee at the Tokyo 2020 Olympics, bagging the much- sought-after top spot by a single point.\", \"from\": 449, \"to\": 591, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 495, \"end\": 504, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matty_Lee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matty Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matty_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matty_Lee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet at the Paris 2024 event, Daley andWilliamsmanaged to bag a silver, but lost out on the gold to China's Lian Junjie and Yang Hao.\", \"from\": 593, \"to\": 725, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 604, \"end\": 614, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 5.645352137856797e-13, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 692, \"end\": 697, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.5058053769464906, \"rank\": 0.6792351742707263, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 700, \"end\": 711, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lian_Junjie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lian Junjie\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lian_Junjie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lian_Junjie\"}, {\"begin\": 716, \"end\": 724, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yang_Hao_(Sui_dynasty)\", \"score\": 0.5916864370255184, \"rank\": 0.40495867768596194, \"text\": \"Yang Hao\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yang_Hao_(Sui_dynasty)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yang_Hao_(Sui_dynasty)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a strong start for Daley and Williams as the diving final kicked off just after 11am local time, with the duo scoring 53.40 in their first dive - which included one and a half somersaults.\", \"from\": 727, \"to\": 922, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At that point, they were tied for the silver medal with Canada, while China were in prime position to bag the gold from the off.\", \"from\": 924, \"to\": 1052, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 980, \"end\": 986, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9971608199907493, \"rank\": 0.0014539628474720618, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 994, \"end\": 999, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.5058053769464906, \"rank\": 0.6792351742707263, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"China had been the favourite to take the gold since before Paris 2024 even began.\", \"from\": 1054, \"to\": 1135, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1054, \"end\": 1059, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.5058053769464906, \"rank\": 0.6792351742707263, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The pair's second dive was dubbed \\\"excellent\\\" by commentators, but they were still left tied with Canada.\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1242, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1235, \"end\": 1241, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9971608199907493, \"rank\": 0.0014539628474720618, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After dive number three, which was the inward three and a half somersaults dive,Tom Daleyand Noah Williams landed five points ahead of Canada, securing the silver position on their own with 188.52 points.\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1448, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1337, \"end\": 1350, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\", \"score\": 0.999998273608197, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Williams\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\"}, {\"begin\": 1379, \"end\": 1385, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9971608199907493, \"rank\": 0.0014539628474720618, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"China continued to take the top spot after the third dive, claiming 199.4 points.\", \"from\": 1450, \"to\": 1531, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1450, \"end\": 1455, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.5058053769464906, \"rank\": 0.6792351742707263, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dive four - the back three and a half somersaults - saw Daley and Williams get a rapturous response from the audience, with commentators suggesting it was \\\"exactly what we needed to see\\\" if the duo were to stay in contention for the gold.\", \"from\": 1533, \"to\": 1771, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the crowd, Daley's husband Dustin Lance Black and his kids Phoenix Rose and Robbie were seen yelling in praise.\", \"from\": 1773, \"to\": 1887, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1803, \"end\": 1821, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_Lance_Black\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dustin Lance Black\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_Lance_Black\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_Lance_Black\"}, {\"begin\": 1835, \"end\": 1842, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\", \"score\": 0.9994302041214629, \"rank\": 0.0005698658982703914, \"text\": \"Phoenix\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\"}, {\"begin\": 1843, \"end\": 1847, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose_Tyler\", \"score\": 0.915233503392124, \"rank\": 0.09107604813599252, \"text\": \"Rose\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose_Tyler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose_Tyler\"}, {\"begin\": 1852, \"end\": 1858, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Hunter-Paul\", \"score\": 0.9672837320546978, \"rank\": 0.03382230391155511, \"text\": \"Robbie\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13415036\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Hunter-Paul\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Hunter-Paul\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dive four landed the duo with 93.96 points, putting them way ahead of the Canadians in pole position to take home the silver.\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 2014, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet China then did \\\"absolutely brilliant\\\", acquiring 95.88 points and a 13 point lead overall.\", \"from\": 2016, \"to\": 2110, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2020, \"end\": 2025, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.5058053769464906, \"rank\": 0.6792351742707263, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The penultimate dive, though not as good as dive four, saw Daley and Williams maintain their silver position.\", \"from\": 2112, \"to\": 2221, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Daley and Williams' final dive was one of their most impressive, bagging a score of 93.24 - and a grand total of463.44.\", \"from\": 2223, \"to\": 2342, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's Daley's fifth Olympic medal, and completes his set - he has now bagged bronze, silver, and gold.\", \"from\": 2343, \"to\": 2444, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"China finished with a staggering total of 490.35.\", \"from\": 2446, \"to\": 2495, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2446, \"end\": 2451, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.5058053769464906, \"rank\": 0.6792351742707263, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Share your thoughts!Let us know in the comments below, and remember to keep the conversation respectful.\", \"from\": 2497, \"to\": 2601, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pleaseloginorregisterto comment on this story.\", \"from\": 2603, \"to\": 2649, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The LGBTQ+ stories you do not want to miss, delivered to your inbox daily.\", \"from\": 2651, \"to\": 2725, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thanks for registering!\", \"from\": 2727, \"to\": 2750, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can update your email subscriptions at any time in theMy profilesection of your account.\", \"from\": 2751, \"to\": 2843, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Related articles  Latest News    What to buy now    Exclusive    Download the PinkNews app  Award winning LGBTQ+ journalism  About us  Editorial Policy  Contact us  Advertise  Work for us    Terms and conditions  Privacy policy\", \"from\": 2845, \"to\": 3072, \"entities\": []}]}"